name: Brandywine Living at Summit
about: Join our family at Summit – a Brandywine senior living community located conveniently near I-78 and just off the Morris Turnpike. Downtown Summit is a hub for families including many fine restaurants, playful shops, and an array of walking paths.At Summit, we offer Serenade, which is a step above in terms of service, amenities, and luxury. Our Serenade program is meticulously designed to surpass expectations and was inspired by a lifestyle with an emphasis on luxury, privacy, and service. Some of our amenities include butler service, cocktail hour, spacious suites, private dining, and intimate lounges.At Summit you can find our residents engaged in a variety of activities. For pure fun, the residents can be found enjoying exciting events including Curtain Call and Karaoke Knights. In fact, Summit offers an abundance of choices for your entertainment and delight.The decision to move into a senior living community is a big one and our team is here to help at every step of the way – please reach out to us if you have any questions or would like more details about our Summit community.

name: Overlook Medical Center
about: Overlook Medical Center was named one of America's 50 Best Hospitals in 2023 by Healthgrades, a 2022 World’s Best Hospital by Newsweek and recognized as a Best Regional Hospital in the NY Metro area by U.S. News & World Report.Our Atlantic Neuroscience Institute is the region’s leader in neuroscience care. A hub for the New Jersey Stroke Network, we offer a broad range of advanced neurological, neurosurgical and neurodiagnostic services. We are also certified as a Level IV Epilepsy Center and home to the Gerald J. Glasser Brain Tumor Center, where more brain tumor surgeries are performed than anywhere else in New Jersey. Our CyberKnife® program is the largest and most experienced in the state.What’s more, we are nationally-recognized in cardiac services by U.S. News and World Report. We provide advanced cardiac imaging, cardiac catheterization, elective PCI and minimally invasive procedures. Furthermore, Overlook is among a select group of hospitals licensed for primary angioplasty.Overlook in 2022 opened the Hersh Children's Center, which provides pediatric inpatient and emergency services in one place.Overlook Medical Center has achieved the prestigious Magnet® recognition. This designation from the American Nurses Credentialing Center is the highest national honor for nursing excellence. What’s more, Overlook Medical Center has advanced certification from The Joint Commission for perinatal care and is designated an Advanced Comprehensive Stroke Center. We also have a satellite emergency department in Union, NJ, which treats about 40,000 emergency cases each year.

name: Summit Transcendental Meditation Program
about: We teach the Transcendental Meditation (TM) technique and follow up programs.  TM is a simple mental technique that produces a profound level of rest that releases stress and produces mental clarity. TM is a universal tool that works because it requires no belief,way of life or mental abilities.  It is easy because we just use the natural tendency of the mind to go to more charming level of the mind.  As a tool, it makes accessing the quieter levels of the mind easier and more consistent.  Over 400 peer reviewed scientific studiesverify benefits for the mind, body and behavior and environment.  Specifically, better mental clarity and focus, released stress and ,better sleep, better health, improved social behavior and reduced violence and crime in the environment when enough people are meditating together collectively.Personal instruction on the first day of a 4 day course involving about an hour and half each day.  Lifetime course fees with monthly payments for those that need it.  Access to local and national group meditations.
